title: Episode 10 - How to Play A Market That's Up 65% In Nine Months
itunes:title: How to Play A Market That's Up 65% In Nine Months
description:
Technology
analyst and Minyanville columnist Michael Comeau breaks down Google and Apple.
Do these tech giants still have room to run? Retirement Millionaire editor
David Eifrig then tells investors where to earn the most interest on their
cash.
